borrow(uint256,uint256).details: Only the owner of a vault can borrow from it. `borrow()` will update the outstanding vault debt to the current time before attempting the withdrawal. `borrow()` will fail if it would bring the vault below the minimum collateralization treshold.

params._amount: the amount of borrowed inceptionCollateral tokens in WEI.*
params._vaultId: the ID of the vault from which to borrow.

deposit(uint256).details: A new vault is created if no vault exists for the `msg.sender` with the specified collateral type. this function uses `transferFrom()` and requires pre-approval via `approve()` on the ERC20.

params._amount: the amount of tokens to be deposited in WEI.*

params._borrowAmount: the amount of borrowed StableX tokens in WEI.*
params._depositAmount: the amount of inceptionCollateral to be deposited in WEI.

depositByVaultId(uint256,uint256).details: this function uses `transferFrom()` and requires pre-approval via `approve()` on the ERC20.

params._amount: the amount of tokens to be deposited in WEI.*
params._vaultId: the ID of the vault in which to deposit the inceptioCollateral.

liquidate(uint256).details: `liquidate()` will update the outstanding vault debt to the current time and pay a `liquidationBonus` to the liquidator. `liquidate()` can be called by anyone.

params._vaultId: the ID of the vault to be liquidated.*

liquidatePartial(uint256,uint256).details: `liquidatePartial()` will update the outstanding vault debt to the current time and pay a `liquidationBonus` to the liquidator. A LiquidationFee will be applied to the borrower during the liquidation. This means that the change in outstanding debt can be smaller than the repaid amount. `liquidatePartial()` can be called by anyone.

params._amount: the amount of debt+liquidationFee to repay.*
params._vaultId: the ID of the vault to be liquidated.

repay(uint256,uint256).details: `repay()` will update the outstanding vault debt to the current time.

params._amount: the amount of PAR tokens in WEI to be repaid.*
params._vaultId: the ID of the vault for which to repay the outstanding debt balance.

repayAll(uint256).details: `repayAll()` will update the outstanding vault debt to the current time.

params._vaultId: the ID of the vault for which to repay the debt.*

params.direct: True if `newOwner` should be set immediately. False if `newOwner` needs to use `claimOwnership`.
params.renounce: Allows the `newOwner` to be `address(0)` if `direct` and `renounce` is True. Has no effect otherwise.

withdraw(uint256,uint256).details: Only the owner of a vault can withdraw collateral from it. `withdraw()` will fail if it would bring the vault below the minimum collateralization treshold.

params._amount: the amount of inceptionCollateral ERC20 tokens to be withdrawn in WEI.*
params._vaultId: the ID of the vault from which to withdraw the inceptionCollateral.

borrow(uint256,uint256).notice: Borrow new PAR tokens from a vault.

claimOwnership().notice: Needs to be called by `pendingOwner` to claim ownership.

deposit(uint256).notice: Deposit inceptionCollateral ERC20 token into the vault of the msg.sender as collateral

depositAndBorrow(uint256,uint256).notice: Deposit inceptionCollateral ERC20 token into the vault of the msg.sender as collateral and borrows the specified amount of tokens in WEI

depositByVaultId(uint256,uint256).notice: Deposit inceptionCollateral ERC20 token into the specified vault as collateral

liquidate(uint256).notice: Liquidate a vault that is below the liquidation treshold by repaying its outstanding debt.

liquidatePartial(uint256,uint256).notice: Liquidate a vault partially that is below the liquidation treshold by repaying part of its outstanding debt.

repay(uint256,uint256).notice: Repay an outstanding PAR balance to a vault.

repayAll(uint256).notice: Convenience function to repay all debt of a vault

transferOwnership(address,bool,bool).notice: Transfers ownership to `newOwner`. Either directly or claimable by the new pending owner. Can only be invoked by the current `owner`.

withdraw(uint256,uint256).notice: Withdraws inceptionCollateral ERC20 token from a vault.
